<bibRefCitation id="EFDF97B4FFC19E1F80D227A33B0A4FC9" author="Martius, CFP" box="[408,634,1670,1696]" pageId="13" pageNumber="74" refId="ref15897" refString="Martius, CFP. von (1827) Nova genera et species plantarum: quas in itinere per Brasiliam MDCCCXVII-MDCCCXX jussu et auspiciis Maximiliani Josephi I., Bavariae regis augustissimi instituto / collegit et descripsit C. F. P. de Martius. Typis Lindaueri, Munich, 121 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 450" type="book" year="1827">Martius (1827: 104)</bibRefCitation>
